31
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,500
and I didn't say anything.

32
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:43,440
Then you decided to attend Xigang,

33
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,860
and I still didn't say anything.

34
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:50,060
But do you know
what your biggest problem is now?

35
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,420
It's your wrist injury.

36
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,420
If you don't heal it properly,

37
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,620
another injury could mean

38
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,860
saying goodbye

39
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,620
to volleyball forever.

40
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,360
You may not like the life

41
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,740
I planned for you,

42
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,820
but how do you know it's bad

43
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,580
if you haven't experienced it?

44
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:24,180
You should at least respect my wishes.

45
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,220
I want you

46
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,580
to go abroad

47
