to think carefully

48
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,020
about what kind

49
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,360
of life you want

50
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,340
while you heal.

51
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,780
Going to school now.

52
